sd-22-dmsms pack — content licence
===================================

This pack is derived from:
    SD-22 DMSMS Guidebook (Diminishing Manufacturing Sources and Material Shortages
        — A Guidebook of Best Practices for Implementing a Robust DMSMS Management Program)
    DSPO (Defense Standardization Program Office), FY24 Working Draft (April 2024)
    Obtained via ASSIST (assist.dla.mil)

Source licence: Public Domain (US Government work); Distribution A  (tier 1 — see ../../docs/SOURCE-VETTING.md)
No source-material download link is published (see ../../docs/LICENSING.md).

This source is a work of the United States Government, prepared under the Defense
