WORKING-DRAFT CAVEAT: the source is the FY24 *working draft* (April 2024). It states
that the reader should check the source to verify it is the current version before use,
and that recommended changes go to the Defense Standardization Program Office. Section,
figure, and table numbers and some guidance may differ in the final FY24 release. This
pack synthesizes the draft's stable content in original wording; it reproduces none of
the source's policy text, tables, figures, or appendix worksheets, and it names DoD
issuances (DoDI 4140.01 / 5000.x / 4245.15, etc.) and appropriations statutes (31 U.S.C.
1502(a), 10 U.S.C. 2213, 10 U.S.C. 4323) only as cited constraints — those issuances and
statutes are themselves US Government works in the public domain.

